      <title>保守党在卑诗省选举中获胜，对手政党瓦解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/conservatives-gain-in-tight-bc-election-race-as-rival-party-disintegrates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本世纪初执政不列颠哥伦比亚省达 16 年之久的政党由于民意调查支持率暴跌而退出了选举。]]></description>
